---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
---

<DefaultLayout
  title="Terms of Service | HugDot"
  description="Terms of Service for HugDot game database."
>
<div class="pp-page">
  <div class="pw">

    <div class="pp-header">
      <h1 class="pp-title">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="pp-date">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pp-sections">

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using HugDot (hugdot.com), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>HugDot provides a free game database covering characters, items, skills, and planning tools for gacha RPGs. These services are provided "as-is" and "as-available" without any warranty of any kind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>3. Game Content & Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All game data, images, and assets displayed on HugDot are the property of their respective owners (HoYoverse, Kuro Games, etc.). HugDot is a fan-made, non-commercial database and is not affiliated with or endorsed by any game publisher.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>4. User Responsibility</h2>
        <p>Users are responsible for how they use the information provided on this site. HugDot makes no guarantees about the accuracy or completeness of game data, as games are updated frequently.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>In no event shall HugDot or its operator be liable for any damages arising out of the use or inability to use this site or its content.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>6. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>Any claim relating to HugDot's website shall be governed by the laws of the Republic of Korea without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pp-section">
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</DefaultLayout>

<style>
.pp-page { min-height:100vh; background:var(--c-bg); color:var(--foreground-color); padding:4rem 0 6rem; }
.pw { max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }
.pp-header { margin-bottom:2.5rem; }
.pp-title { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-bottom:.4rem; }
.pp-date { font-size:.75rem; color:var(--c-muted); }
.pp-sections { display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
.pp-section { padding:1.5rem 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--c-border); }
.pp-section:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.pp-section h2 { font-size:.95rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--c-accent); margin-bottom:.6rem; }
.pp-section p { font-size:.82rem; color:var(--c-muted); line-height:1.85; word-break:keep-all; }
.pp-section a { color:var(--c-accent); text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:3px; }
.pp-section a:hover { opacity:.8; }
</style>